ComicInfo.Summary:
Forty years ago superstar glamour model Kendra Rhoades disappeared from the American media circus, giving up her life to live anonymously in Europe. When Nostalgia Magazine brokers a deal with her for her return, they hire Private Detective Jennifer Mays to retrieve her from the airport and confirm her identity. But when she arrives, three different women claim to be the former model. Things go from bad to worse when one of the Kendras retains Jen's old friend and rival private detective Devlin Brooks who ends up murdered. Now it's up to Jen and Gabe to solve the murder and the real identity of Kendra Rhodes before the murderer claims another victim.
